Welcome to Cash Flow's documentation!¶

Cash Flow Main¶

Register¶

Allows user to register for an account after they provide a valid username, email, and password.

Login¶

Allows user to login to an account that they created.

Logout¶

Allows user to logout of an account that they're currently logged into.

Navigation Bar¶

Allows user to navigate to other web pages on the website.

Input Credit Card¶

Allows user to input credit card information such as their current cash back options and the amount they spend per month.

Delete Credit Card¶

Allows users to delete credit cards that they no longer need.

Compare Credit Cards¶

Allows user to see other credit cards that are confirmed to be good, and see if other cards are better or not.

Admin Page¶

Allows admin users to delete and create new credit cards that users can compare their current credit cards to.
